**who —** The Dachora — the large, ostrich-like creature that races back and forth to build speed and launch itself skyward — demonstrating the Speed Booster's Shinespark — and another life Samus can save on the way out

**what —** the large, ostrich-like creature that races back and forth to build speed and launch itself skyward — demonstrating the Speed Booster's Shinespark — and another life Samus can save on the way out

